{
  "texts": [
    "In a design-centric approach, for example, Adepu and Mathur [31] captured the design using state condition graphs.",
    "It was used to capture the conditions on actuation w.r.t.",
    "sensor readings, expressed using Boolean conditions, and represented in a graphical format.",
    "The work in Yoong et al. [32] used axiomatic design methodology for systems, where it iteratively decomposes a CPS design to sets of dependent components and transformed into invariants.",
    "The work in Raman and Mathur [33] has a detection rate of over 90% against actuators and above 75% against sensors, excluding certain stealth attacks."
  ]
}